Class Mood

java.lang.Object
com.example.cmput301_team_project.Mood

Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
MoodAnger, MoodConfusion, MoodDisgust, MoodFear, MoodHappiness, MoodSadness, MoodShame, MoodSurprise
public abstract class Mood extends Object implements Serializable
Base class for mood event. Use createMood(MoodEmotionEnum, MoodSocialSituationEnum, String, String, Date, String) factory method to create the correct subclass instance of the base class
